# Noetfield — AUTO CONFLICT RESOLUTION (all agents)

**When any rules conflict → run SKILL-007 before disk edits.**

## Precedence (short)

1. **Founder current message** (explicit bounded order)
2. **R-001–R-009** hard rules (permission, ask-first, scope, SourceA block)
3. **Open P0/P1 incidents**
4. **`execution_authority: false`** (advise only)
5. **Workflow bundles** (PLAN WITH NO ASF — only after founder approves)
6. **Ship-first / plan.json** — never self-start

## Hard law

> Ship-first and no-ASF **never** override R-007 (permission) or R-008 (ask first).

## On conflict

1. Stop — no edits
2. Name both rules + winner
3. Propose A/B/C
4. **ASK founder**
5. Implement only bounded T0 order

